# Honesty fence (CRITICAL — preserved verbatim):
#   - The 23 n6-* "domain application" papers have ABSTRACT MATCH RATES
#     ranging 89-100% EXACT — but a Texas Sharpshooter z=0.74 baseline
#     for individual matches is acknowledged in MULTIPLE abstracts
